trans-unit.source: Gets the assembly that uses the <see cref="T:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary" /> object referenced by the <see cref="P:System.Windows.Diagnostics.ResourceDictionaryInfo.ResourceDictionaryAssembly" /> property.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o assembly que usa o objeto <see cref="T:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary" /> referenciado pela propriedade <see cref="P:System.Windows.Diagnostics.ResourceDictionaryInfo.ResourceDictionaryAssembly" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the resource dictionary for which additional information is described by this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Diagnostics.ResourceDictionaryInfo" /> object instance.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o dicionário de recursos para os quais informações adicionais são descritas por esta instância do objeto <see cref="T:System.Windows.Diagnostics.ResourceDictionaryInfo" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the name of the assembly from which the resource dictionary is loaded.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o nome do assembly do qual o dicionário de recurso é carregado.

trans-unit.source: Gets the URI of the compiled BAML file embedded in the <see cref="P:System.Windows.Diagnostics.ResourceDictionaryInfo.ResourceDictionaryAssembly" /> property from which the resource dictionary is loaded.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o URI do arquivo BAML compilado inserido na propriedade <see cref="P:System.Windows.Diagnostics.ResourceDictionaryInfo.ResourceDictionaryAssembly" /> da qual o dicionário de recursos é carregado.
